[[Image:KateVernon.jpg|thumb|250px|Kate Vernon as the scheming [[Ellen Tigh]] on ''[[Battlestar Galactica (2004 TV series)|Battlestar Galactica]]'']]
'''Kate Vernon''' (born c. [[1961]]) is a [[Canada|Canadian]]-born film and television actress. She is best known for her role as Lorraine Prescott on the [[CBS]] [[soap opera]] ''[[Falcon Crest]]'' from (1984 - 1985), and for her role as the stuck -up Benny Hanson in the [[comedy film]] ''[[Pretty in Pink]]'' (1986).

Vernon also played the scheming [[Lady Macbeth]]-like [[Ellen Tigh]] on ''[[Battlestar Galactica (2004 TV series)|Battlestar Galactica]]'' until her character was killed in season 3.

Her father was actor [[John Vernon]], and her sister is singer/actress [[Nan Vernon]].

